After a while, the rural scenery that had spread all around
was gradually adorned by the urban skyscrapers.

The period known as winter vacation passed by quickly in a
short amount of time.

However, what remains vividly in \n[1]'s memories is that the
days spent in the Ichinose family were all irreplaceable.
Yui, Rio, Miyuki, and many friends they met in the city---

The promise that leads to the future that he exchanged with
them \c[14] gradually swelled up in \n[1]'s heart as a great
expectation.

While gazing at the scenery outside the car window, I long
for the arrival of spring.

In order to create even more vivid memories in spring,
following summer and winter---

So that the bonds with them can grow even stronger and
stronger---

\n[1] closes his eyes while looking back on the irreplaceable
days with them---
\n[1]: \c[14] I will come to play again, okay? \|\|\^
